"title": "8023: faith, necessity of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8023",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A fundamental duty for all people and the necessary response to God's self-revelation. The only channel through which God's blessings may be received, and the only means by which life may be made meaningful, in relationship with God.</p>\n<h2>The call to faith</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3-Ps37:5\">PSA 37:3–37:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:10\">ISA 50:10</a></p>\n<h3>In the NT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:28-John6:29\">JHN 6:28–6:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30-Acts16:31\">ACT 16:30–16:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:4\">ACT 19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:21\">ACT 20:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:5\">ROM 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:23\">1JN 3:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's self-revelation leaves no excuse for unbelief</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:8-John14:11\">JHN 14:8–14:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:17-Rom10:18\">ROM 10:17–10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:4\">PSA 19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10-John1:12\">JHN 1:10–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:21\">ROM 1:18–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:1-Rom3:4\">ROM 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:27\">ROM 16:25–16:27</a></p>\n<h2>The need for faith in God</h2>\n<h3>The LORD is the only true God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18-Hab2:20\">HAB 2:18–2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:2-Ps115:11\">PSA 115:2–115:11</a></p>\n<h3>God alone can be trusted absolutely</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1-Ps91:4\">PSA 91:1–91:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Faith in God is the basis for peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:11\">PSA 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1-2Pet1:2\">2PE 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Faith is necessary to receive God's blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:4\">PSA 40:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7-Jer17:8\">JER 17:7–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></p>\n<h3>Faith is necessary to avoid God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18\">JHN 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:12\">2TH 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:6–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a></p>\n<h2>Actions not springing from faith are sinful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:23\">ROM 14:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:5-Rom14:8\">ROM 14:5–14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:14\">ROM 14:14</a></p>\n<h2>Unbelief challenged</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:18\">HEB 3:12–3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:8\">PSA 95:7–95:8</a> <em>comparison with the Israelites in the wilderness</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:9\">ISA 7:9</a> <em>Ahaz, king of Judah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5-Jer17:6\">JER 17:5–17:6</a> <em>the people of Judah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:14\">MRK 16:14</a> <em>Jesus Christ's disciples after the resurrection</em></p>",
